-align: -0.338ex; width:6.301ex; height:2.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle m&g=
t;0}"></span>.</li>
<li>A "decreasing" or "descending" line goes <em>down</em> from left to rig=
ht and has negative slope: <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element=
