t;0}"></span>.</li></ul>
<p>Special directions are:
</p>
<ul><li>A "(square) <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diagonal" titl=
e=3D"Diagonal">diagonal</a>" line has unit slope: <span class=3D"mwe-math-e=
lement mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-m=
