<li>A "horizontal" line (the graph of a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org=
/wiki/Constant_function" title=3D"Constant function">constant function</a>)=
 has zero slope: <b><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline=
"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"disp=
lay: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{=
\displaystyle m=3D0}">
  <semantics>
