ent" data-file-width=3D"609" data-file-height=3D"462"></a><figcaption>Slope=
 illustrated for <span class=3D"nowrap"><i>y</i> =3D (3/2)<i>x</i> =E2=88=
=92 1</span>. Click on to enlarge</figcaption></figure>
<figure class=3D"mw-halign-right" typeof=3D"mw:File/Thumb"><a href=3D"https=
