class=3D"den">d<i>x</i></span></span> =3D 2<i>x</i></span>. So the slope of=
 the line tangent to <i>y</i> at (=E2=88=922,4) is <span class=3D"nowrap">2=
 =E2=8B=85 (=E2=88=922) =3D =E2=88=924</span>. The equation of this tangent=
